AtriStation ATR-01
==================

Vendor: leftymods
Product: AtriStation
Model: ATR
Version: 01
SoC: Amlogic SM1 / S905X3

This board port is based on the existing SM1 AC223 U-Boot support and keeps a
minimal U-Boot bring-up surface: serial, storage, USB/update, Android boot flow,
and the SM1 DDR/firmware support inherited from the source board.

Device tree files:

* atr_01_android_full.dts - full Android DTS text ported from the supplied
  S905X2/G12A source to SM1/S905X3 metadata. The original LED ring nodes are
  preserved.
* atr_01_uboot_minimal.dts - minimal U-Boot-oriented DTS text with only board
  identity and LED ring I2C devices.
